
Ranger Help for: reconnoiter(recon)
===================================

SYNTAX:      reconnoiter <direction>/reconnoiter far <direction>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   7
BASE SP:     40 sp
SKILL TYPE:  knowledge

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to take in information, such as sound, smells
and keen eyesight to get an idea of what creatures are in the direction
that the Ranger reconnoiters. Extra perceptive Rangers can sense 
far(two rooms aways).

